"144" slineno="2-47" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1066" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(d)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="156" groupid="113" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">the interest rates charged, consistent with the requirements of Subsection <xref depth="4" refnumber="4-18-110(6)">(6)</xref>.</amend></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="3-37" dnum="_-o:5-i" numlevel="1" lineno="145" slineno="2-48" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1067" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(5)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="182" groupid="129" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">In fixing interest rates, the commission shall consider:</amend><subsection ssid="3-38" dnum="_-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="146" slineno="2-49" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1068" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="187" groupid="133" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">the current applicable interest rate or rates being charged by the USDA Farm Service <ln numlevel="1" lineno="147" slineno="2-50"/>Agency on similar loans;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="3-39" dnum="_-o:b-i" numlevel="1" lineno="148" slineno="2-51" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1069" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="192" groupid="137" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">the current prime rate charged by leading lending institutions; and</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="3-40" dnum="_-o:c-i" numlevel="1" lineno="149" slinen